癸.definition: tenth of the ten Heavenly Stems 十天干[shi2 tian1 gan1]; tenth in order; letter "J" or Roman "X" in list "A, B, C", or "I, II, III" etc; ancient Chinese compass point: 15°; deca

癸丑.definition: fiftieth year J2 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1973 or 2033

癸亥.definition: sixtieth year J12 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1983 or 2043

癸卯.definition: fortieth year J4 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1963 or 2023

癸巳.definition: thirtieth year J6 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 2013 or 2073

癸未.definition: twentieth year J8 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 2003 or 2063

癸酉.definition: tenth year J10 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1993 or 2053
